-- Bahrain Employment Rises in 2011 as Pay Climbs, al-Hayat Reports
-- B y   W a e l   M a h d i
-- 2012-06-19T09:47:59Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-19/bahrain-employment-rises-in-2011-as-pay-climbs-al-hayat-reports.html
Bahrain employment, including locals
and expatriates, rose 3.1 percent in 2011 from the previous year
to 618,037, al-Hayat reported, citing Labor Minister Jameel
Humaidan.  The average monthly salary climbed 11.5 percent to $1,300
in the fourth quarter last year from a year earlier, the pan-
Arab  newspaper  said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Wael Mahdi in Manama at 
 wmahdi@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
